    ('Arma', 'Shooter', 39.99, 'A military simulation game offering a realistic combat experience in a sandbox environment. Known for its extensive mod support and complex gameplay.', 'arma_image.png', 'pc','https://www.youtube.com/embed/HuFuTbAxw9o?si=_mDmOhqxdX5IjGc'),
